ololive Productions 活跃了大约 5 年零 8 个月，是整个 VTuber 行业的资深人才. 是不可替代的。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="从 Hololive 1 代到粉丝" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oE8HLVwpimA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><p>而 Mel Yozora 为 Hololive Productions 和整个 VTuber 行业留下的许多东西，也将在未来继续支持许多人才。</p><p>我衷心希望Cover的这一重要决定能够对公司、Hololive Productions旗下的人才以及VTuber行业的未来产生积极的影响。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"> https://www.youtube.com/live/n8sbwz0sir0?si=iATuAQdhg-ystzfb</div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCD8HOxPs4Xvsm8H0ZxXGiBw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">梅尔频道 Yozora 梅尔频道</a>/ <a href="https://twitter.com/yozoramel" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Yozora 梅尔<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f31f.png" alt="🌟" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Hololive 第一代</a>/ <a href="https://hololive.hololivepro.com/talents/yozora-mel/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Yozora Mel</a></p> <cite>YouTube / X（推特）/ Hololive Production</cite></blockquote><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://cover-corp.com/news/detail/20240116" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">关于解除《Yozora Mel》合同的通知</a></p><cite>封面有限公司</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“Mr.2”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="kxeSdc4Slc"